图片合成: 基于VueDRR拖拽功能, 在其上通过叠加图片、文字等, 实现图片的: Image Composition: Based on VueDRR's drag-and-drop feature, it overlays images, text, etc., to achieve image overlay and pseudo-composition functionality.
ImageCompress: 纯JS实现对图片的等比压缩和放大的功能, 并能对图: ImageCompress: Pure JS implementation of proportional compression and enlargement of images, with the ability to download images.
React-CountUp: 一个无依赖、轻量级的react数字滚动插件, 以更: React-CountUp: A dependency-free, lightweight React plugin for scrolling numbers, displaying numerical data in a more interesting way.
React-CodeMirror: 是一款基于 react 的代码编辑器, 可支: React-CodeMirror: A code editor based on React, supporting languages like HTML, JavaScript, TypeScript, etc.
antv-g6: 一个图可视化引擎。它提供了图的绘制、布局、分析、交互、动画等图: antv-g6: A graph visualization engine that provides basic capabilities for drawing, layout, analysis, interaction, animation, etc., in graph visualization.
react-tree-org: 基于 react 的树结构组织图, 可用于公司组: react-tree-org: A tree structure organizational chart based on React, suitable for displaying company organizational structures.
wangEditor: 基于javascript和css开发的 Web富文本编辑: wangEditor: A web rich text editor developed based on JavaScript and CSS. Lightweight, simple, easy to use, and open source.
React-Md-Editor: 是一款基于 react 的 Markdown: React-Md-Editor: A Markdown editor based on React, suitable for blog systems.
